{
  "texts": [
    "We directly address this open question, demonstrating that introspective behavior can be robustly trained using transient injections.",
    "Unlike prior steering work focused on control (e.g., reducing toxicity), we use steering as a stimulus for learned awareness.",
    "Self-modeling [Binder et al., 2024] ---n/a Propensity awareness [Betley et al., 2025] ---n/a Concept injection [Lindsey, 2025] ✓ -global ∼20% Our work ✓ ✓ single-token 85% Self-Knowledge and MetacognitionResearch on model self-knowledge includes uncertainty estimation [Kadavath et al., 2022, Lin et al., 2022] and self-modeling [Laine et al., 2024, Binder et al., 2024].",
    "Betley et al. [2025] and Plunkett et al.",
    "[2025] show models can describe their own learned propensities."
  ]
}